### ================================
### BASE URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ================================
### 1. REGISTER ADMIN
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### ================================
### 2. LOGIN ADMIN
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### ================================
### 3. GET SEMUA ASPIRASI (DASHBOARD)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/aspirasi
Authorization: YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### ================================
### 4. INPUT ASPIRASI (SISWA)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/aspirasi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nis": 12345,
  "id_kategori": 1,
  "lokasi": "Kelas 10",
  "ket": "Kursi rusak"
}

###

### ================================
### 5. HISTORY SISWA
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/aspirasi/history/12345

###

### ================================
### 6. UPDATE STATUS + FEEDBACK (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/aspirasi/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "Proses",
  "feedback": "Sedang diperbaiki"
}

